title: You probably can’t hit max clock speeds on AMD’s Ryzen 9 7950X
description: AMD Ryzen 9 7950X is going to have a high maximum clock speed, but most of us won't be able to achieve it -- here's why.

title: This Microsoft Teams exploit could leave your account vulnerable
